# Only the Dockerfile and wikitext-103-raw-v1/ need to go into the
# build context. Excluding everything else keeps the context small
# (~520 MB instead of ~520 MB + venv + checkpoints + ...) and avoids
# busting the COPY layer cache on unrelated edits.
*
!Dockerfile
!wikitext-103-raw-v1/
!wikitext-103-raw-v1/wiki.train.raw
!wikitext-103-raw-v1/wiki.valid.raw
!wikitext-103-raw-v1/wiki.test.raw
